# SQL Course Exercises

This repository contains my solutions for the SQL course exercises completed using the PostgreSQL **dvdrental** sample database.

## Tools Used

- PostgreSQL 18
- DBeaver Community Edition
- Git & GitHub
- Python (Exercise 15 Automation)

